| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1602 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d6ae878e-5cff-59c7-b345-c6c2b4bac55f"
